abstract: >-
  The Mooduel Movie Database contains structured mood profiles for 30,611
  movies spanning 1888-2026. Each movie is scored across 18 psychological
  dimensions including valence, arousal, dominance, absorption potential,
  hedonic/eudaimonic/psychologically-rich valence, emotional arc, pacing,
  ending type, comfort level, watch context, and vibe sentence. Classified
  using Claude Haiku 4.5 from TMDB metadata, Wikipedia plots, Rotten
  Tomatoes critic reviews, TMDB user reviews, and MovieLens Tag Genome.
